title: ‘Trump Bump’ for Dow Industrials Is Biggest Post-Inaugural Move Since FDR
text: President has been doing a lot of bragging about the stock market rally lately. How does it measure up? By some measures, the rally that took place during Mr. Trump’s first 30 calendar days in office has been the largest for any president’s first month on the job since 1945. Since inauguration day on Jan. 20   Stocks to Watch: Home Depot, Advanced Auto Parts, Bristol-Myers
